ans another branch, another deploy.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"problem-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"problem-icon amber\",\"children\":\"⚠\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"No fallback on failure\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"A provider goes down and your users get 500s. You hardcoded one model — there’s no plan B unless you build one.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"problem-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"problem-icon orange\",\"children\":\"↑\"}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Context lost between turns\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Even if you route well on the first message, continuations land on a different model. KV caches are wasted and conversations break.\"}]]}]]}]]}]\n7:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"landing-section\",\"id\":\"how-it-works\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-label\",\"children\":\"How It Works\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"section-heading\",\"children\":\"Configure once. Route every request.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"section-desc\",\"children\":[\"You define your model catalog with guidance on when to use each model. The router’s LLM classifier reads every incoming prompt and matches it to the right model from \",[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"your\"}],\" list.\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-container\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-step\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-marker\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-number\",\"children\":\"01\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-line\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flow-content\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"children\":\"Define your model catalog\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"List the models you want available. For each one, describe when it should be used, its strengths, and its capabilities. This is yo